    "title": "Installed electricity capacity (with allocated shares, by state)",
    "description": "Same as the geographical-location capacity, but with each state credited its share of joint-sector and central-sector plants according to the regional allocation formulas. This is the figure you should use when comparing 'how much electricity does this state have rights to' rather than 'how much physical capacity is sited there'.",
